          <declname>out_state</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Queries the activity state of a sound input. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The state of sound inputs can be either MLAudioState_Playing or MLAudioState_Stopped, depending on whether MLAudioStartInput or MLAudioStopInput was called most recently. When an input is stopped and restarted, its buffers are emptied and buffering begins again from a clean slate.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">handle</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>MLHandle of the sound input. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">out_state</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>MLAudioState enum of the sound input.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<parameterlist kind="retval"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MLResult_InvalidParam</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Failed due to an invalid parameter. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MLResult_Ok</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Successfully retrieved the properties. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
